thread.title: Vicki

author: Vicki
title: Vicki
text: After a long search for a specific type of TV stand in oak wood I came upon Oak Furnitureland and was so pleased to find many options. Their site is very easy to navigate and thorough with dimensions and description. Their prices are excellent for such high quality furniture. This is SOLID WOOD furniture- NOT particle board or veneer. I am so happy with this purchase and will definitely order from them again!
